s": 38, "replies": 9, "retweets": 6, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 2, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066348854107087123", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066348854107087123", "text": "The expected drop in oil prices on the headlines is happening, but this war did cause damage that’s not being reflected yet in the price. One thing that took the market by surprise is the impact of price manipulation. #OOTT https://t.co/qUQBWbPYrN", "time": "02:35", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 47007, "likes": 411, "replies": 34, "retweets": 35, "quotes": 4, "bookmarks": 14, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2066352680566448605", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066352680566448605", "text": "Now that the “deal is done”… who will be left to mop up the mess and damage caused by the conflict? #OOTT", "time": "02:50", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 14059, "likes": 100, "replies": 12, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Geopolitics", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066364912440422833", "url": "https://x.com/Amena__Bakr/status/2066364912440422833", "text": "We are celebrating status quo (IF it even happens) @ianbremmer #OOTT", "time": "03:39", "author": "Amena__Bakr", "author_name": "Amena Bakr", "followers": 174705, "views": 21672, "likes": 120, "replies": 9, "retweets": 13, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Iran", "Tankers/shipping"]}}, {"id": "2066368590928810057", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066368590928810057", "text": "Strait of Hormuz oil backlog could take weeks to clear after US-Iran deal\nPrices slip even as analysts warn flows may be slow to recover and remain vulnerable to renewed disruption #oott \nhttps://t.co/YVjaKgV5iF", "time": "03:53", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 7565, "likes": 82, "replies": 8, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 11, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066373672961515786", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066373672961515786", "text": "Oil Executives Are Sounding the Alarm Over Dwindling Stockpiles\nEven if the Strait of Hormuz soon reopens, it would likely take months for the U.S. to replenish its depleted oil inventories, keeping prices elevated #oott https://t.co/W5p0stNUIe", "time": "04:14", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 10835, "likes": 83, "replies": 6, "retweets": 23, "quotes": 5, "bookmarks": 12, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["US inventories", "Supply outlook"]}}, {"id": "2066403099523051950", "url": "https://x.com/staunovo/status/2066403099523051950", "text": "Brent futures curve in USD/bbl (today, one week ago and one month ago) #OOTT https://t.co/wTPXoFFCTt", "time": "06:11", "author": "staunovo", "author_name": "Giovanni Staunovo🛢", "followers": 120883, "views": 13622, "likes": 34, "replies": 0, "retweets": 10, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 7, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Neutral", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2066413339320914386", "url": "https://x.com/JuneGoh_Sparta/status/2066413339320914386", "text": "Let's see how this plays out.\n\n#oott", "time": "06:51", "author": "JuneGoh_Sparta", "author_name": "June Goh", "followers": 18022, "views": 9995, "likes": 77, "replies": 6, "retweets": 18, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 20, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Tankers/shipping", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066466433656332737", "url": "https://x.com/ElephantCapita2/status/2066466433656332737", "text": "#USOIL update. Wrong on this so far. 67-75 in scope first. Need to revisit longs when that area is met. \n\n#OOTT $USO #OIL https://t.co/lZWbMtCQvv", "time": "10:22", "author": "ElephantCapita2", "author_name": "Elephant Capital", "followers": 14976, "views": 13659, "likes": 25, "replies": 1, "retweets": 0, "quotes": 1, "bookmarks": 8, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_sentiment": "Neutral", "topics": ["Prices/technicals"]}}, {"id": "2066483014570279215", "url": "https://x.com/SamanthaLaDuc/status/2066483014570279215", "text": "EIA: even if shipments resume in 3Q26, a return to pre-conflict traffic isn’t expected until early 2027. #OOTT\n\nAnd that’s assuming the Iran War actually ends… color me skeptical.", "time": "11:28", "author": "SamanthaLaDuc", "author_name": "Samantha LaDuc", "followers": 72749, "views": 8270, "likes": 100, "replies": 4, "retweets": 9, "quotes": 0, "bookmarks": 6, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bullish", "emotional_sentiment": "Negative", "topics": ["Supply outlook", "Iran"]}}, {"id": "2066546606854295655", "url": "https://x.com/LiveSquawk/status/2066546606854295655", "text": "#OOTT | Senior US Official: US Has Signed MOU With Iran\n- President Trump, VP Vance Signed MOU, So Did Iranian Parliamentary Speaker\n- Deal Provides For Immediate Opening Of Strait And Lifting Of US Blockade\n- Strait Opening Takes A Little Bit Of Time Because Of Mines\n- Expect Increase In Hormuz Flo", "time": "15:41", "author": "LiveSquawk", "author_name": "LiveSquawk", "followers": 436347, "views": 8987, "likes": 14, "replies": 6, "retweets": 5, "quotes": 2, "bookmarks": 0, "labels": {"relevant": true, "price_sentiment": "Bearish", "emotional_se